---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import heroImage from '../assets/images/model7.png';

const anchors = [
  ['Verified Provenance', 'A named, ongoing partnership with Ercole Moretti, not a vague "inspired by Venice" claim.'],
  ['Hands-On Restoration', 'I personally restore every vintage piece, preserving its history instead of erasing it.'],
  ['Lifetime Warranty', 'Every piece is backed against defects, because I stand behind what I make.'],
  ['Real Conversations', 'Questions get answered by me, on the phone or by message - not a script.'],
];
---

<Layout
  title="About Rosario Leonardi Murano Glass"
  description="The story behind Rosario Leonardi Murano Glass and its direct, verifiable sourcing relationships."
>
  <Nav />
  <main>
    <section id="hero" class="relative overflow-hidden bg-ink px-6 pb-24 pt-40 text-white sm:px-10">
      <img
        src={heroImage.src}
        alt=""
        class="absolute inset-0 h-full w-full object-cover"
        aria-hidden="true"
      />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-ink/70" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-[1040px]">
        <div class="mb-8 flex items-center gap-4">
          <div class="h-px w-6 bg-gold"></div>
          <span class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-gold">About</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="mb-7 font-display text-[48px] font-light leading-none tracking-normal md:text-[78px]">
          From Venice Glassmakers to You.
        </h1>
        <p class="max-w-[740px] font-sans text-[16px] font-light leading-[1.85] text-white/68">
          The story behind Rosario Leonardi Murano Glass - and why authenticity isn't just a selling point, it's the whole point.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-parchment px-6 py-24 sm:px-10">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-[1180px] gap-12 lg:grid-cols-[0.9fr_1.1fr]">
        <h2 class="font-display text-[42px] font-light leading-none text-ink md:text-[64px]">Real Relationships, Not Just Real Glass.</h2>
        <div class="space-y-6 font-sans text-[16px] font-light leading-[1.9] text-ink-soft">
          <p>Authentic Murano glass isn't something you stumble into. It comes from real relationships with real artisans - the kind built over years, not algorithms.</p>
          <p>That's exactly why I partner directly with Ercole Moretti, one of the most exclusive bead designers in Venice. Every piece I create starts there - with glass that has a verifiable origin, not a guess.</p>
          <p>Alongside my original designs, I personally source and restore vintage Murano Millefiori pieces, bring uncirculated treasures back from my European supplier relationships, and curate freshwater pearls for those who want the same integrity in a different form.</p>
          <p>This isn't a warehouse. It's not a dropship operation. It's one person - me - making sure what reaches you is actually what I say it is.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-white px-6 py-24 sm:px-10">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-[1180px] gap-12 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_1fr] lg:items-center">
        <div>
          <div class="mb-6 flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="h-px w-6 bg-gold"></div>
            <span class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-gold">Mission</span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-[42px] font-light leading-none text-ink md:text-[64px]">Why I Care So Much About "Real."</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-6 font-sans text-[16px] font-light leading-[1.9] text-ink-soft">
          <p>The online market for Murano glass is flooded with mass-produced imports and vague sourcing claims. I've seen too many people get burned - paying real money for something that isn't what it claims to be.</p>
          <p>I'd rather be the seller who proves it, every time, than the seller who just says "trust me."</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-parchment px-6 py-24 sm:px-10">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1180px]">
        <h2 class="mb-12 font-display text-[42px] font-light leading-none text-ink md:text-[64px]">What Makes This Different</h2>
        <div class="grid gap-px border border-rule bg-rule md:grid-cols-2">
          {anchors.map(([title, body]) => (
            <article class="bg-white p-8">
              <h3 class="mb-4 font-display text-[28px] font-normal leading-tight text-ink">{title}</h3>
              <p class="font-sans text-[14px] font-light leading-[1.85] text-ink-soft">{body}</p>
            </article>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-ink px-6 py-24 text-white sm:px-10">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1040px]">
        <h2 class="mb-7 font-display text-[42px] font-light leading-none md:text-[64px]">Whether You're Collecting, Gifting, or Creating -</h2>
        <p class="mb-8 max-w-[760px] font-sans text-[16px] font-light leading-[1.9] text-white/70">
          I built this shop for the people who care about getting it right: collectors who want provenance, families looking for a gift that actually means something, and makers who need materials they can trust. Whoever you are, I'd love to help you find the piece that's actually yours.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <a href="/shop" class="bg-white px-6 py-3 font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-ink transition-colors hover:bg-gold-light">Shop the Collection</a>
          <a href="/contact" class="border border-white/25 px-6 py-3 font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-white transition-colors hover:border-gold hover:text-gold-light">Get in Touch</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
